1. Deadlock is the situation when two thread are in waiting state and waiting for another thread to provide lock of another object.

2. In java deadlock situation comes because of synchronized block

Starvation :- When there is a long wait for any thread before it get processor from thread Schedular is called starvation.

Like if we have 1 cr thread and only 1 thread has priority of 1 all other has 10.So that thread will be get a chance in last.